title: Magnified Docs
description: You'll find all types of Accordion which is both use for HTML, REACTJS and NEXTJS

body.raw:
<Tabs defaultValue="preview" className="w-full  relative ">
  <TabsList>
    <TabsTrigger value="preview">Preview</TabsTrigger>
    <TabsTrigger value="codesnippet">Code</TabsTrigger>
  </TabsList>
  <TabsContent value="preview">
    <ComponentPreview name="tab3" category="component" />
  </TabsContent>
  <TabsContent value="codesnippet">
    <CodeWrapper noExpand={true}>
      <CodePreview name="tab3" category="component" />
    </CodeWrapper>
  </TabsContent>
</Tabs>

#### Installation

```bash
npm install framer-motion
```

```js title="tooltip.tsx"
'use client'

import { cn } from '@/lib/utils'
import * as TooltipPrimitive from '@radix-ui/react-tooltip'
import * as React from 'react'

const TooltipProvider = TooltipPrimitive.Provider

const Tooltip = TooltipPrimitive.Root

const TooltipTrigger = TooltipPrimitive.Trigger

const TooltipContent = React.forwardRef<
  React.ElementRef<typeof TooltipPrimitive.Content>,
  React.ComponentPropsWithoutRef<typeof TooltipPrimitive.Content>
>(({ className, sideOffset = 4, ...props }, ref) => (
  <TooltipPrimitive.Portal>
    <TooltipPrimitive.Content
      ref={ref}
      sideOffset={sideOffset}
      className={cn(
        'z-50 overflow-hidden rounded-lg border bg-background backdrop-filter dark:border-[#2C2C2C] backdrop-blur-lg dark:bg-[#1A1A1A]/95 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-popover-foreground shadow-md animate-in fade-in-0 zoom-in-95 data-[state=closed]:animate-out data-[state=closed]:fade-out-0 data-[state=closed]:zoom-out-95 data-[side=bottom]:slide-in-from-top-2 data-[side=left]:slide-in-from-right-2 data-[side=right]:slide-in-from-left-2 data-[side=top]:slide-in-from-bottom-2',
        className
      )}
      {...props}
    />
  </TooltipPrimitive.Portal>
))
TooltipContent.displayName = TooltipPrimitive.Content.displayName

export { Tooltip, TooltipTrigger, TooltipContent, TooltipProvider }
```

function MagnifiedDocOneFile() {\r
  const mouseX = useMotionValue(Infinity)\r
  const [index, setIndex] = useState(0)\r
  const [prevIndex, setPrevIndex] = useState(0)\r
\r
  const handleClick = (i: React.SetStateAction<number>) => {\r
    setPrevIndex(index)\r
    setIndex(i)\r
  }\r
\r
  const isForward =\r
    index > prevIndex || (index === 0 && prevIndex === apps.length - 1)\r
\r
  return (\r
    <>\r
      <div className="relative [box-shadown]  rounded-xl  dark:bg-gray-950 bg-gray-300  [box-shadow:inset_1px_-1px_4px_rgba(0_0_0,0.5)] overflow-hidden ">\r
        <div className="relative">\r
          {apps.map((app, i) => {\r
            return (\r
              <>\r
                <AnimatePresence mode={'popLayout'}>\r
                  {index === i && (\r
                    <motion.div\r
                      initial={{\r
                        opacity: 0,\r
                        y: isForward ? 30 : -30,\r
                      }}\r
                      animate={{\r
                        opacity: 1,\r
                        y: 0,\r
                      }}\r
                      exit={{\r
                        opacity: 0,\r
                        y: isForward ? -30 : 30,\r
                      }}\r
                      transition={{\r
                        type: 'ease',\r

                        duration: 0.3,\r
                        delay: 0.4,\r
                      }}\r

            )\r

\r

            <div className="w-fit mx-auto">\r
              <TooltipProvider delayDuration={0}>\r
                <motion.div\r
                  onMouseMove={(e) => mouseX.set(e.pageX)}\r
                  onMouseLeave={() => mouseX.set(Infinity)}\r
                  className="mx-auto flex sm:h-[57px] h-[52px] w-fit items-end gap-2 rounded-t-lg px-2 pb-2 dark:bg-gray-800/80 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm border-t border-l border-r  "\r
                >\r
                  {apps.map((app, i) => {\r
                    return (\r
                      <Tooltip key={app.id}>\r
                        <TooltipTrigger onClick={() => handleClick(i)}>\r
                          <span className="sr-only">{app.name}</span>\r
                          <AppIcon mouseX={mouseX} src={app.icon} />\r
                        </TooltipTrigger>\r
                        <TooltipContent\r
                          className="py-1 px-3 rounded-sm"\r
                          sideOffset={8}\r
                        >\r
                          <p className="text-xs">{app.name}</p>\r
                        </TooltipContent>\r
                      </Tooltip>\r
                    )\r

              </TooltipProvider>\r

          </div>\r
        </div>\r
      </div>\r
    </>\r
  )\r
}\r
\r
function AppIcon({ mouseX, src }: { mouseX: MotionValue; src: any }) {\r
  const ref = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null)\r
\r
  const distance = useTransform(mouseX, (val) => {\r
    const bounds = ref.current?.getBoundingClientRect() ?? { x: 0, width: 0 }\r
\r
    return val - bounds.x - bounds.width / 2\r
  })\r
\r
  const widthSync = useTransform(distance, [-100, 0, 100], [40, 55, 40])\r

    stiffness: 150,\r
    damping: 12,\r
  })\r

        src={src}\r

        height={60}\r
        alt=""\r
        quality={100}\r
        ref={ref}\r
        style={{ width }}\r
        className="aspect-square rounded-lg sm:w-8 w-6  object-cover"\r
      />\r
    </>\r
  )\r
}\r
export default MagnifiedDocOneFile\r
